title: 050 - Simple Zeet
description: On today's show, the guys check in on the legitimacy of KFC buffets, dive into some #PodFacts, chat about if they could last 100+ hours without falling asleep for $1,000,000, Rita's Italian Ice, Belgium chocolate, where the definition of SIMP comes from, and everything else that pops up. It's a fun one. Enjoy.
